        Welcome to my personal website. I'm an iOS developer, entrepreneur, and open source contributor.
      </p>
      <p class="text-foreground/80">
        I'm the founder and CEO of <Link href="https://pspdfkit.com" external underline>PSPDFKit</Link>, a company that provides PDF solutions for web, mobile, and desktop applications. 
        Our technology is used by thousands of companies worldwide to power their document workflows.
